  "lyrics": "You know it's down the road You know you gotta keep going on When it feels right You know you gotta keep moving in I know you know you want it I see the way I'm gonna shake it I'm looking at me You know you gotta go, come get it You know that you just want it all That is what you feel in me You know, I know That you just gotta go, gotta get it Anytime you want it, baby, I'll yell I'll help you, let you fall I'll live a life of fear I got the strength, fear of you, I got it You know you wanna come, go get it Come on, get it when it ain't You know you wanna come, let me down I know you're here for me, oh yeah Come on, come and get your taste of me I feel so good when you're near, oh Yeah, I feel like you're the one To change me, to make me, erase me, complete me I think that you know that we're here, oh, completely Oh, if you're somewhere else, oh, find you Oh, fucking find you Hi, hi, hi, I don't know",
